> 
> 2.4.8-34.1mdk boots fine however.
> 
> I'm about to go try 2.4.16 (it was working with reiserfs partitions
> before).
> 
> The machine is an AMD Athalon 1.3 Ghz on an EPOC board with a 3ware 7800
